cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with 3D object detection using LIDAR point clouds and RGB-images. It may also belong to Robotics (cs.RO) as 3D object detection is an important task in robotics. Additionally, the paper proposes a novel fusion approach and a multi-task network, which may fall under the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper also involves semantic segmentation, which is a common task in Natural Language Processing (cs.CL).
